title: Syrian military video shows soldiers in eastern Ghouta after rebels leave
text:
Syrian military video shows soldiers in eastern Ghouta after rebels leave Monday, March 26, 2018 - 00:46 
Syrian military video appears to show soldiers walking through the town of Ain Tarma in eastern Ghouta after rebels purportedly retreated. Rough cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
